<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <script
      src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/cddaf0c0ff.js"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:ital,wght@0,300;0,700;1,700&family=Open+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,300;1,700&family=Poppins:wght@200;300;400;500;600;700&family=Roboto+Flex:opsz,wght@8..144,300;8..144,500;8..144,700;8..144,900&family=Roboto:wght@300;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-iYQeCzEYFbKjA/T2uDLTpkwGzCiq6soy8tYaI1GyVh/UjpbCx/TYkiZhlZB6+fzT"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-u1OknCvxWvY5kfmNBILK2hRnQC3Pr17a+RTT6rIHI7NnikvbZlHgTPOOmMi466C8"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.9.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css"
    />
    <title>Primeiro Acesso | Pref. de Salto</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-light">
    <style>
      #yes.valid {
        background-color: green;
        color: #fff;
      }

      #yes.invalid {
        background-color: red;
        color: #fff;
        animation: glitch forwards 0.25s ease-in-out;
      }

      @keyframes glitch {
        0% {
          transform: translateX(10px);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateX(-20px);
        }
        100% {
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }
      .btn {
        background-color: #8a40b4;
        color: #fff;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .feedback.invalid,
      .feedback-email.invalid,
      .feedback-confirm {
        color: red;
      }

      .feedback.valid,
      .feedback-confirm.valid,
      .feedback-email.valid {
        color: green;
      }

      @media screen and (min-width: 897px) {
        .form-group {
          width: 33%;
          margin: auto;
        }
      }
    </style>
    <div class="container">
      <div
        class="d-flex-align-items-center justify-content-center flex-column mb-3"
      >
        <div class="mb-2 w-100 text-center p-5">
          <p class="h1">
            Olá <span style="color: #8a40b4"><%= name.split(' ')[0] %> </span>,
            seja bem-vindo(a).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3 w-100 text-center">
          <p class="text-muted fs-5">
            Este é seu primeiro acesso. Recomendamos que efetue o cadastro de um
            email e a troca da sua senha para sua segurança e o funcionamento de
            algumas funções do aplicativo.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="matricula" class="form-label fs-5 fw-bold"
              >MATRICULA:</label
            >
            <input
              type="text"
              name="matricula"
              id="matricula"
              class="form-control p-2"
              disabled
              value="<%= matricula %>"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label fs-5 fw-bold">EMAIL:</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              class="form-control p-2"
              name="email"
              id="email"
              placeholder="example@example.com"
              required
            />
            <div class="form-text feedback-email"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="password" class="form-label fs-5 fw-bold"
                >NOVA SENHA:</label
              >
              <input
                type="password"
                name="password"
                id="password"
                class="form-control p-2"
                min="8"
                placeholder="Mínimo de 8 caracteres."
                required
              />
              <div class="form-text feedback"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="confirmPassword" class="form-label fs-5 fw-bold">
                CONFIRME A NOVA SENHA:
              </label>
              <input
                type="password"
                name="confirmPassword"
                id="confirmPassword"
                class="form-control p-2"
                required
              />
              <div class="form-text feedback-confirm"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3 w-100">
              <button class="btn p-3 w-100" id="yes">Confirmar.</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/firstAccess.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
